@$OpenBSD: patch-libtiff_tif_next_c,v 1.5 2016/01/24 16:48:49 naddy Exp $

* libtiff/tif_next.c: fix potential out-of-bound write in NeXTDecode()
triggered by http://lcamtuf.coredump.cx/afl/vulns/libtiff5.tif
(bugzilla #2508)

